{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a5c3c09eaa","title":"在颐年堂的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c76100f81d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":2,"day":16,"articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"姚文元","id":"92a8a42842","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"0f4aad7e2f","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是中央宣传工作会议之前主席召开的一次座谈会，对文、哲、教育界谈文化思想问题，着重谈文学批评问题。这一材料根据三份传达记录稿整理而成，以一份记录稿为主，括号内是根据另两份记录稿插入的。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6df9f3b0aa","type":"title","text":"在颜年堂的讲话！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0f4aad7e2f","type":"paragraph","text":"今天谈文学艺术、学术思想等百家争鸣的方针问题，文艺有了缺点，应当如何对待。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8263cdd462","type":"paragraph","text":"王蒙写了一篇小说，赞成他的很起劲，反驳他的也很起劲，但是反驳的态度不怎么适当","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dda01eb03c","type":"paragraph","text":"（王蒙的《组织部新来的年轻人》正在讨论，问题在于批评态度。小说揭发官主义，很好，揭发得不深刻，但很好。刘宾雁的小说并没有批评整个官主义。王蒙的小说有片面性，正面的积极力量写得不够，要批评。应该有批评，也应该有保护。正面人物林震写得无力，而反面人物很生动。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"01ef0a3000","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的官主义就是没有整跨，应该批评。过去有一个片子（指《荣誉属于谁》）没有演，那不是因为批评了老干部，要保护老干部，而是因为在那个片子里，那官主义没有整跨。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6debe27ceb","type":"paragraph","text":"《星星》（四川的诗刊）里面有几首诗还是好的，有几首是不好的，要酸酿一下，不要骂。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d1e63b4e4","type":"paragraph","text":"（《星星》在叫喊，不要忙，沉住气，酸酿一下，不要仓皇应战，不打无准备之仗，过去的“批评”文章，群众投我们的票少。）","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"472e2c828c","type":"paragraph","text":"对那些写了环作品的作者要帮助，要调查","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de2f3df89f","type":"paragraph","text":"对起义将领傅作义，对荣毅仁，我们都是帮助、改造。这样做了，他们就同我们合作。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b39f49014a","type":"paragraph","text":"环小说，无非里面有资产阶级思想，唯心论，只要作者在政治上同我们合作，就和胡风有区别，不能一根子打死。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b6051d6ed","type":"paragraph","text":"王蒙是不会写。他会写反面人物，可是正面人物写不好。写不好，有生活的原因，有观点的原因","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2f48a7f9c2","type":"paragraph","text":"李希凡说主蒙写的地方不对，不是典型环境，说北京在中央，不可能出现这样的问题，这是不能说服人的。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba3d1940d2","type":"paragraph","text":"中央里面就出过环人，像张国寿、高、饶、李立三、王明。环人多了怎么办？照他们的办法就要用油锅煮。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a09f8ee452","type":"paragraph","text":"李希凡的文章不能说服人，认为中央所在地的区委不会有官机主义，是不对的。中央都出过高、饶，区委（有官主义）更不稀奇了，“难免论”嘛。（对林震也有些“难免论”。）】","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"89412ce315","type":"paragraph","text":"对如何处理人民内部的错误的方针，很多同志实际没懂。对这个方针，十个部长大概有九个反对。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce774a4cbc","type":"paragraph","text":"【问题是作者（王蒙）对人民内部矛盾问题没有搞清楚，所以小说有消极影响。我们也没有搞清楚。因为写北京，（地方）太具体，就不是典型环境中的典型性格，这样（批评）不能说服人。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"250570b565","type":"paragraph","text":"王蒙的小说有小资产阶级思想，他的经验也还不够，但他是新生力量，要保护，批评他的文章没有保护之意。","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c2b1fe529","type":"paragraph","text":"是有官主义。我们党的威望大，靠党的威望，官主义就横行霸道，违法乱纪，是不是应该揭发？","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"99dd031b2b","type":"paragraph","text":"中国是一个小资产阶级的大王国，小资产阶级一共有五亿五十万之多·....·这也是客观实际。","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b27e0c114c","type":"paragraph","text":"（中国是小资产阶级大王国，党内也不可能没有小资产阶级。）","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e06f512eb4","type":"paragraph","text":"说共产党的缺点不能揭发，这种观点不对。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"985c89e11d","type":"paragraph","text":"党的统一战线政策，实际赞成的人很少，真正懂得的人很少，“整”，不能服人。","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"85f41ed3dd","type":"paragraph","text":"（十部中真正搞通统一战线思想的人不多——要帮助人家改造，达到真正的团结。怎样帮助改造人家思想，很不够，办法常是整一通。“整”，很容易，但不是好办法，应不用。“整”，不能团结。）","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"93d506b7a0","type":"paragraph","text":"现在王明还是有选票，他还是中华人民共和国的公民，而不是一脚把他踢倒","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"99548935f8","type":"paragraph","text":"“一脚踢倒”是老办法，那很容易。喜欢用这办法的人，最好开枪，开机关枪，那是国民党的办法。","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7583924fcc","type":"paragraph","text":"（小资产阶级天王国是客观现实。工人阶级只有两千四百方，其中产业工人占一半，干部也占一半，这是一头；另一头是地富和资产阶级，大约有三千万；中间五亿五千万都是小资产阶级。一千两百方十部也并不都是无产阶级化的，真正化了的大约有二百方。所以，看文艺问题要从这现实出发。）","index":25,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1b15369f1d","type":"paragraph","text":"现在是大变的时期，有的人不满。农业合作化，富裕中农就不满。中","index":26,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ed6921abd7","type":"paragraph","text":"（大学生中地富和资产阶级子弟占80%，都是非工人阶级，青年问题多，并不奇怪。其中要搞牙利事变的极少，多数是拥护共产主义的。）","index":27,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d6ed02b50","type":"paragraph","text":"但是，不满的人过去还是拥护抗美援朝，他们不搞“牙利”。当然，个别想搞牙利事变的人也是有的。","index":28,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6744326ce2","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的同志就是怕，怕牙利事件。我看牙利事件也没有什么不好。要讲辩证法，要懂得事物的两面性，不这么一闹，就没有真正好的勾牙利。","index":29,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b481bb9435","type":"paragraph","text":"（·矛盾总要表面化，闹一闹还是好的。闹是片面性，我们用片面性去反对片面性，不能解决问题。）","index":30,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"442f7c73ab","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的同志有教条主义，用片面性反对片面性，用形而上学反形而上学。","index":31,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9adf983b77","type":"paragraph","text":"王蒙的小说有片面性，又有反官主义的一面，我看他的文章写得相当好，不是很好。","index":32,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a10d77e181","type":"paragraph","text":"他暴露了我们的缺点，不能用季希凡那样的批评","index":33,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f583811050","type":"paragraph","text":"（许多批评文章，立场对，但简单化。）","index":34,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"152506d84c","type":"paragraph","text":"李希凡现在在高级机关，当了政协委员，吃光饭，听党的命令，当了婆婆，写的文章就不生动了，使人读不下去。文章的头平截，使人读不懂。","index":35,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6b7f3e976a","type":"paragraph","text":"马寒冰是什么人？也是一个什么官长，总是一个什么军长级的干部吧，他在《文汇报》的文章就写得不好，教条主义。","index":36,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf94f961a7","type":"paragraph","text":"【陈其通等四人的文章，立场很好，《人民日报》也可以发表，但是说服不了人，似乎百花齐放以后都错了，这是教条主义，朵朵香花是不可能的。教条主义是没有力量的，它所以滋长，原因之一是共产党当了政。马克思、恩格斯批评杜林，列宁批评卢那卡尔斯基，所以要下功关，验倒他们。斯天林不同，（他当了政），所以他们批评不平等，很容易，像老子骂儿子。“一朝权在手，便把令来行”。批评不要利用当政的权力，需要真理，用马克思主义，下功夫，是能战胜的。","index":37,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"24be982fc1","type":"paragraph","text":"（用教条主义不能批评人家，因无力量，请看一下列宁是如何写《经验批判论》的。斯大林后来就不同了，不是平等讨论问题了，不是搜集大量材料发表意见。有些东西写得好，有些东西只坐在山岗上，捡起石头打人，使人看了后不大舒服。）","index":38,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7af878d26","type":"paragraph","text":"陈其通、马寒冰等四人联名写的文章，后讲清楚原因，没有办法。陈沂，你写了几篇文章？有没有教条主义？出一个选集吧！全面检查一下。","index":39,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94b1307f43","type":"paragraph","text":"教条主义的文章干巴巴，简单化，不能说服人","index":40,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e55acce9a7","type":"paragraph","text":"教条主义滋长，是因为当了政。","index":41,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9dbd40e6bf","type":"paragraph","text":"马、恩驳杜林，很用了一番心思。但是当了政的斯大林就不一样了，他骂人不平等，没有说服力。","index":42,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1f5510fd12","type":"paragraph","text":"应该研究分析人家的文章。","index":43,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d108a3a8bf","type":"paragraph","text":"当了政，骂人像骂儿子一样，不好。","index":44,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f479eae95c","type":"paragraph","text":"当政党同人民的关系，不应当是老爷同人民的关系，不应该骂","index":45,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2572236348","type":"paragraph","text":"教条主义不是马克思主义","index":46,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34b201caab","type":"paragraph","text":"过去批评胡适，取得很大的成功，开头我们说，不能全抹杀部适，他对中国的启蒙运动起了作用。康有为、梁启超也不能抹杀。","index":47,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aad4227da8","type":"paragraph","text":"胡适说，我是他的学生。他当教授，我当小职员，工资不一样，但我不是他的学生。","index":48,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"03eae8ae3e","type":"paragraph","text":"现在不必恢复胡适的名誉，到二十一世纪再来研究这个问题吧","index":49,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"54881e5cda","type":"paragraph","text":"（过去因为是斗争，所以讲缺点，今大也不必平反。今大他是帝国主义走狗，到二十一世纪，历史上还是要讲清楚的。）","index":50,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"32058a5dda","type":"paragraph","text":"（对地富、资产阶级要安排、改造，何况对小资产阶级？我们写文章常常笔下不留情。教条主义的本领是戴帽子、骂人、片面性，不是从团结出发，目的也不是团结。不是帮助改造缺点，达到真正的团结。）","index":51,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f7b9def68e","type":"paragraph","text":"（对人民内部的错误，要同对付故人的错误严格地区别，错误的杂文也是不区别。对敌人无情斗争，对人民是从团结出发，经过斗争达到新的团结，否则就容易系人。）","index":52,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1299c884a8","type":"paragraph","text":"应当“刀下留人”","index":53,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a11e23b9b8","type":"paragraph","text":"过去延安整风，我们不是说过“燕前感后，治病救人”吗？我们有些同志不喜欢治病救人，而是唐医系人。对小资产阶级应当用适当的方法将他们改造。（那么多小资产阶级，我们靠他们吃饭，要把他们改造为工人阶级。）我们有百分之五六十的同志不了解中央这个方针：批评团结，治病救人","index":54,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2be69ff0a2","type":"paragraph","text":"他们就是怕闹事。","index":55,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"db24246a8a","type":"paragraph","text":"清华有个学生，说要系几千万人，这太多了。这个学生也不要开除他的学籍。","index":56,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e9e80695a4","type":"paragraph","text":"学生闹事有理由，但也不提倡大医课。他们反国民党反成了习惯。","index":57,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"df0d5ce440","type":"paragraph","text":"不允许工人黑工是不正确的。宪法上没禁止害工。贴标语是言论自由，开会是集会自由。","index":58,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c10585b9b1","type":"paragraph","text":"对闹事的人不应当通通叫他们写梅过书，也不要写检讨","index":59,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f54620a041","type":"paragraph","text":"因为有问题，还是闹一下好。","index":60,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f954a20c86","type":"paragraph","text":"学生闹事，不等于造反。","index":61,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9e3e0f9c12","type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人，一年有一百万人闹事是正常的，六百分之一。","index":62,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf5071ada3","type":"paragraph","text":"闹事的人根本不能说是反革命，可能其中有个别反革命。","index":63,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"524202d375","type":"paragraph","text":"对付官主义，最好是黑工、医课、打扁担，因为老不解决问题哟！","index":64,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"63572c6d4b","type":"paragraph","text":"当然，我也不登广告，提倡全国要工","index":65,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f245a65028","type":"paragraph","text":"这些矛盾是暂时性的矛盾，不是根本性的矛盾。","index":66,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"13a342a980","type":"paragraph","text":"出了事情，要看两面。（闹事的人也有两面性，警惕我们。有肽疮，出旅就好了。）","index":67,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"382d259a7d","type":"paragraph","text":"说老子是“老革命”不能反对。国民党也是“老革命”，比我们更老。我们不能采取国民觉对人民的态度。","index":68,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b5b9744307","type":"paragraph","text":"马克思主义是同敌人作斗争发展起来的，同资产阶级思想作斗争，从资产阶级思想内，取合理的部分，发展起来，这样才形成了马克思主义。","index":69,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f35302ffdc","type":"paragraph","text":"现在的危险是以为天下太平了，因此看见王蒙的批评就不高兴。只是打，是锻炼不出文学艺术来的。","index":70,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5b8374eb6a","type":"paragraph","text":"是不是允许查花，不允许毒草存在？（百花齐放应允许毒草存在，允许风格不同。）","index":71,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f014a4b9e4","type":"paragraph","text":"毒草是毒人的，但是香花是同毒草作斗争才发展起来的。","index":72,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c211e80f94","type":"paragraph","text":"粮食地里有许多野草，庄称是同野草作斗争才发展起来的。苏联建设了几十年社会主义，地里一样有野草。有野草不要紧，一翻过来，就是肥料。","index":73,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"517c997df2","type":"paragraph","text":"是毒草，可以说明，有的人主张写：“此是毒草，不许尝试。”苏联的办法是只要香花，不要毒草。其实许多毒草是借香花之名以生。我们的主张是：毒草与香花齐放，落霞与孤签齐飞。","index":74,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3330789d28","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林有唯心论，有唯物论，他有片面性。（形而上学，有唯心也有唯物，斯大林两者都有，有辩证法，也有形而上学。正因为这样，所以有功有过，功大于过。）","index":75,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c566bb740","type":"paragraph","text":"苏联同志转不过来，喜欢采用高压的办法","index":76,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7fa8091520","type":"paragraph","text":"教条主义的方法，就是形而上学的方法。","index":77,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3835968ab8","type":"paragraph","text":"对王蒙作品赞美、骂，都是片面性","index":78,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee796e2f35","type":"paragraph","text":"王蒙有两重性，一是好处，一是缺点。","index":79,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"633c8fc1ce","type":"paragraph","text":"一点里有两点，一个事物包含有两个不同的侧面。","index":80,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d9579c86d4","type":"paragraph","text":"商品有二重性，王蒙也有二重性。","index":81,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6574313936","type":"paragraph","text":"《文汇报》上姚文元的文章好。（《教条与原则》很有说服力。）","index":82,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da5907ecd0","type":"paragraph","text":"不能说以前都是教条主义。国民党曾经一家独鸣，所以打倒他们后，共产党也有一阵一家独鸣，这个一家独鸣是必需的，现在就不同了。","index":83,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45b311d0bf","type":"paragraph","text":"（东欧出乱子，就是这原因。现在情况变了，必须百家争鸣。要争鸣就要有准备。通过鸣来教育改造，而不是自由主义。一切不要一脚踢开，对错误要批评，也要承认二重性。）","index":84,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4009566fd6","type":"paragraph","text":"可以对大家讲清楚，不要仓促应战，不要仓促写文章。打仗，不是说不打无准备的仗，不打没有把握的仗吗？没有把握的也就是无准备的。现在打的仗也就是无准备的。","index":85,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"39cec1e4bd","type":"paragraph","text":"有资产阶级、地主、富农的线余，有从那里出来的小资产阶级知识分子，有思想斗争，有对他的教育责任","index":86,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"61e4cfed98","type":"paragraph","text":"我们现在是以少数教育多数","index":87,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"57a791080c","type":"paragraph","text":"不要用简单的办法开除","index":88,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a396a6bb86","type":"paragraph","text":"他们可以当教员，很难找到这样的教员。","index":89,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d0c820f35","type":"paragraph","text":"马寒冰、李希凡的文章也有二重性，是教条主义，但可以促起注意。他们实际不赞成百花齐放、百家争鸣的方针。","index":90,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"61855c5171","type":"paragraph","text":"实际，一万年以后还有非马克思主义。","index":91,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74f9ab349f","type":"paragraph","text":"而且，有一天马克思主义自己也要完毕。五百年以后怎样设想？现在五百年当过去多少万年。","index":92,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1cd895c610","type":"paragraph","text":"将来的世界，阶级斗争完了，马克思主义有些东西就没有用了。","index":93,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc892ca3f5","type":"paragraph","text":"宣布自己是永恒真理，就不是马克思主义","index":94,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d83160a636","type":"paragraph","text":"将来没有阶级斗争，但有新的斗争。那时社会科学领域内总会有新的学说出来。","index":95,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"930c4a89d3","type":"paragraph","text":"当然，有些东西是不能推翻的，如同说地球旋转而太阳不旋转，是地球绕着太阳转，而不是太阳绕着地球转。但是地球有一天还是要烂的。","index":96,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1badcce7d9","type":"paragraph","text":"人类也会被否定。有一天这样的人类不适合了，就一切毁灭，但这样对宇宙进化有好处。","index":97,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"81eb2116ff","type":"paragraph","text":"三千年前，人类还用石头，以后进化到用铜铁，一直到用机器。人类历史五十万年，章太炎在“书”里就讲过。铜器时代否定了石器时代，人类在地球上就是挖地皮过日子。谁也没有选举人类当地球的主人，许多动物，野兽没有选，细菌也没有选，大概只有植物才不反对我们。我们死了，可以供给植物养料，我们排泄的东西也可以供它们补用","index":98,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"35f7a7c802","type":"paragraph","text":"人类本身要进化，马克思主义者也要进步。","index":99,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fe80b44bba","type":"paragraph","text":"如何建设这样一个大国家，是马克思主义者的一个新问题。如何少走弯路？我们这样一个大国，六亿人口，马克思没有想到，列宁也没有想到，他建设社会主义国家也没有几年","index":100,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6af5b7521e","type":"paragraph","text":"我们六亿人口，将来有一天上街，在大街上走都得排队。将来在街上会挤杀人，怎样分配报纸，怎样看电影，怎样逛公园，都会成问题。","index":101,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2a39be2d59","type":"paragraph","text":"不能说一切问题都解决了，还有很多问题要发现，要解决","index":102,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"269146f5c8","type":"paragraph","text":"不要怕歪风。风总有两种，一歪一正。","index":103,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"218cf644c8","type":"paragraph","text":"吉林今年大水灾，就是下多了雨。两股流，一股寒流，一股暖流，不在黑龙江上空相遇，也不在辽宁上空相遇，偏偏在吉林上空相遇，作战，就下大雨。雨下多了，不好。但是如果不下雨，就是早灾。两股还缺不得一股。","index":104,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d28e8173df","type":"paragraph","text":"越斗争，越丰富，就会出现新道理。","index":105,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ab7416526f","type":"paragraph","text":"（口口：现在有一种倾向，写爱情多。）","index":106,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b5162e242f","type":"paragraph","text":"没有爱情，人类就会绝种","index":107,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bd574294f6","type":"paragraph","text":"（口口：杂文有“难免论”。）","index":108,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"724ecca95c","type":"paragraph","text":"“难免论”要多登几篇，这样就引起注意了。","index":109,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5a1ed5e493","type":"paragraph","text":"掌握政权也有两重性。许多人就是怕“放”，怕“鸣”。","index":110,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a7c9cf7b86","type":"paragraph","text":"（我们应特别注意到，掌握政权之后，想用简单的办法把人打倒。百花齐放为什么有人怕放？怕饭票子过河。青年人反对官主义不那么怕，因为他们还没有当事，官主义还未轮到他们头上。）","index":111,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"223ed7a705","type":"paragraph","text":"最近这种压法，缺之说理，不大妙，应给人家出路、帮助。","index":112,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"549e3cb62b","type":"paragraph","text":"口口：王蒙要求谈。）","index":113,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4b14d4c902","type":"paragraph","text":"谈两点：1.好，反官主义；2.文章还有缺点。","index":114,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e4f366a1bb","type":"paragraph","text":"王蒙很有希望，新生力量，有文才的人难得","index":115,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"79858aedcb","type":"paragraph","text":"现在就是碰不得官主义，好像骂官主义就是骂自己，好，你自己既然承认官主义，就得骂。","index":116,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"068da17966","type":"paragraph","text":"不能讲北京不能批评，不能讲不能写党的缺点","index":117,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8fd143a49a","type":"paragraph","text":"（口口：说不搞工农兵了。）","index":118,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a08e0c03b","type":"paragraph","text":"不搞了，全国就剩下工农兵加知识分子了","index":119,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d44ee9a62","type":"paragraph","text":"（口口：工农兵搞得好，大家还是欢迎。）","index":120,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3541f9aa60","type":"paragraph","text":"是啊，我们反杜林反了许多年，还不知道杜林是怎样的，可不可以找到杜林的书？","index":121,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d8dfd9aa2","type":"paragraph","text":"（口口：谈到辩证逻辑和形式逻辑的关系。）","index":122,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9168b4e2b5","type":"paragraph","text":"黑格尔、马赫。《新建设》周谷城论大逻辑，有点道理。","index":123,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"225b5e698b","type":"paragraph","text":"（学校只听校长意见，不听学生意见不对。）","index":124,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":288,"end":279}},"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"013786cb69","type":"paragraph","text":"〔《星星》在叫喊，不要忙，沉住气，酝酿一下，不要仓皇应战，不打无准备之仗，过去的“批评”文章，群众投我们的票少。〕","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"063d83fe93","type":"paragraph","text":"王蒙是不会写。他会写反面人物，可是正面人物写不好。写不好，有生活的原因，有观点的原因。","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"06d18027f2","type":"paragraph","text":"吉林今年大水灾，就是下多了雨。两股流，一股寒流，一股暖流，不在黑龙江上空相遇，也不在辽宁上空相遇，偏偏在吉林上空相遇，作战，就下大雨。雨下多了，不好。但是如果不下雨，就是旱灾。两股还缺不得一股。","index":109,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"070d4887e7","type":"paragraph","text":"人类本身要进化，马克思主义者也要进步。","index":104,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"076fa95e7f","type":"paragraph","text":"〔......矛盾总要表面化，闹一闹还是好的。闹是片面性，我们用片面性去反对片面性，不能解决问题。〕","index":31,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"08ef7342cb","type":"paragraph","text":"〔中国是小资产阶级大王国，党内也不可能没有小资产阶级。〕","index":19,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0e9e899802","type":"paragraph","text":"过去延安整风，我们不是说过“惩前毖后，治病救人”吗？我们有些同志不喜欢治病救人，而是庸医杀人。对小资产阶级应当用适当的方法将他们改造。〔那么多小资产阶级，我们靠他们吃饭，要把他们改造为工人阶级。〕我们有百分之五、六十的同志不了解中央这个方针：批评团结，治病救人。","index":56,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0faec97cb4","type":"paragraph","text":"马克思主义都是同敌人作斗争发展起来的，同资产阶级思想作斗争，从资产阶级思想内，取合理的部分，发展起来，这样才形成了马克思主义。","index":71,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1003ef3e7b","type":"paragraph","text":"学艺术来的。","index":73,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1075ebec1d","type":"paragraph","text":"掌握政权也有两重性。许多人就是怕“放”，怕“鸣”。","index":115,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11cfecb7ae","type":"paragraph","text":"谈两点：1．好，反官僚主义；2．文章还有缺点。","index":120,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"12d9a02ce4","type":"paragraph","text":"将来的世界，阶级斗争完了，马克思主义有些东西就没有用了。","index":97,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"14f579e463","type":"paragraph","text":"（××：工农兵搞得好，大家还是欢迎。）","index":126,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"15783d8b38","type":"paragraph","text":"今天谈文学艺术、学术思想等百家争鸣的方针问题，文艺有了缺点，应当如如对待。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"174eff4c11","type":"paragraph","text":"不允许工人罢工是不正确的。宪法上没禁止罢工。贴标语是言论自由，开会是集会自由。","index":60,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1848f331a7","type":"paragraph","text":"不要用简单的办法开除。","index":92,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"18b0b23def","type":"paragraph","text":"学生闹事有理由，但也不提倡大罢课。他们反国民党反成了习惯。","index":59,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a695f4ef2","type":"paragraph","text":"学生闹事，不等于造反。","index":63,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a7b000829","type":"paragraph","text":"〔对地富、资产阶级要安排、改造，何况对小资产阶级？我们写文章常常笔下不留情。教条主义的本领是戴帽子、骂人、片面性，不是从团结出发，目的也不是团结。不是帮助改造缺点，达到真正的团结。","index":52,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1e2115f6a5","type":"paragraph","text":"应该研究分析人家的文章。","index":44,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"213571ab50","type":"paragraph","text":"实际，一万年以后还有非马克思主义。","index":95,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"218bfa00a7","type":"paragraph","text":"现在不必恢复胡适的名誉，到二十一世纪再来研究这个问题吧。","index":50,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"21f4f81530","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林有唯心论，有唯物论，他有片面性。〔形而上学，有唯心也有唯物，斯大林两者都有，有辩证法，也有形而上学。正因为这样，所以有功有过，功大于过。〕","index":78,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2480319652","type":"paragraph","text":"但是，不满的人过去还是拥护抗美援朝，他们不搞“匈牙利”。当然，个别想搞匈牙利事变的人也是有的。","index":29,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"28019d859d","type":"paragraph","text":"（××：谈到辩证逻辑和形式逻辑的关系。）","index":128,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"28e3455a8e","type":"paragraph","text":"王蒙写了一篇小说，赞成他的很起劲，反驳他的也很起劲，但是反驳的态度不怎么适当。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2c1cde8867","type":"paragraph","text":"苏联同志转不过来，喜欢采用高压的办法。","index":79,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2df04e0abc","type":"paragraph","text":"〔小资产阶级大王国是客观现实。工人阶级只有二千四百万，其中产业工人占一半，干部也占一半，这是一头；另一头是地富和资产阶级，大约有三千万；中间五亿五千万都是小资产阶级。一千二百万干部也并不都是无产阶级化，真正化了的大约有二百万。所以，看文艺问题要从这现实出发。〕","index":26,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30804ceed1","type":"paragraph","text":"不能讲北京不能批评，不能讲不能写党的缺点。","index":123,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30ba02abdf","type":"paragraph","text":"对王蒙作品赞美、骂，都是片面性。","index":81,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"31566ba3ce","type":"paragraph","text":"（××：杂文有“难免论”。）","index":113,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"320b054aa7","type":"paragraph","text":"〔对人民内部的错误，要同对付敌人的错误严格地区别，（错误的杂文也是不区别）。对敌人无情斗争，对人民是从团结出发，经过斗争达到新的团结，否则就容易杀人。〕","index":53,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3229258d96","type":"paragraph","text":"马、恩驳杜林，很用了一番心思。但是当了政的斯大林就不一样了，他骂人不平等，没有说服力。","index":43,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"32a7eccd40","type":"paragraph","text":"对付官僚主义，最好是罢工、罢课、打扁担，因为老不解决问题吆！","index":66,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33890f362c","type":"paragraph","text":"有资产阶级、地主、富农的残余，有从那里出来的小资产阶级知识分子，有思想斗争，有对他的教育责任。","index":90,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3460060c66","type":"paragraph","text":"越斗争，越丰富，就会出现新道理。","index":110,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3501b3d318","type":"paragraph","text":"〔问题是作者（王蒙）对人民内部矛盾问题没有搞清楚，所以小说有消极影响。我们也没有搞清楚。因为写北京，（地方）太具体，就不是典型环境中的典型性格，这样（批评）不能说服人。〕","index":15,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3760a201b5","type":"paragraph","text":"他暴露了我们的缺点，不能用李希凡那样的批评。","index":34,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"386b1d9897","type":"paragraph","text":"中央里面就出过坏人，像张国焘，高、饶、李立三、王明。坏人多了怎么办？照他们的办法就要用油锅煮。","index":12,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3fa148e162","type":"paragraph","text":"清华有个学生，说要杀几千万人，这太多了。这个学生也不要开除他的学籍。","index":58,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40a1eaba74","type":"paragraph","text":"中国是一个小资产阶级的大王国，小资产阶级一共有五亿五千万之多，......这也是客观实际。","index":18,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40ea806e70","type":"paragraph","text":"应当“刀下留人”。","index":54,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40efdbc28b","type":"paragraph","text":"当了政，骂人像骂儿子一样，不好。","index":45,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"41eb3d9c5c","type":"paragraph","text":"不搞了，全国就剩下工农兵加知识分子了。","index":125,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"42e8119f42","type":"paragraph","text":"不是太阳绕着地球转。但是地球有一天还是要烂的。","index":101,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"44eff3dbc8","type":"paragraph","text":"〔许多批评文章，立场对，但简单化。〕","index":35,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4585c7827e","type":"paragraph","text":"〔黑格尔、马赫。新建设周谷城论大逻辑，有点道理。〕","index":129,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"48d4922720","type":"paragraph","text":"毒草是毒人的，但是香花是同毒草作斗争才发展起来的。","index":75,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e5345ad2a","type":"paragraph","text":"（××：现在有一种倾向，写爱情多。）","index":111,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4eb13a86ff","type":"paragraph","text":"“一脚踢倒”是老办法，那很容易。喜欢用这办法的人，最好开枪，开机关枪，那是国民党的办法。","index":24,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4fbed5f64b","type":"paragraph","text":"〔学校只听校长意见，不听学生意见不对。〕","index":130,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"503d3c19a9","type":"paragraph","text":"“难免论”要多登几篇，这样就引起注意了。","index":114,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5258cd3058","type":"paragraph","text":"宣布自己是永恒真理，就不是马克思主义。","index":98,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"57f3c3d51e","type":"paragraph","text":"（××：说不搞工农兵了。）","index":124,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"599b6b7b4f","type":"paragraph","text":"最近这种压法，缺乏说理，不大妙，应给人家出路，帮助。","index":118,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5a7aabe9c2","type":"paragraph","text":"他们可以当教员，很难找到这样的教员。","index":93,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5ed4b35e23","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的同志就是怕，怕匈牙利事件。我看匈牙利事件也没有什么不好。要讲辩证法，要懂得事物的两面性，不这么一闹，就没有真正好的匈牙利。","index":30,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5eee5f68df","type":"paragraph","text":"而且，有一天马克思主义自己也要完毕。五百年以后怎样设想？现在五百年当过去多少万年。","index":96,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6091c49aee","type":"paragraph","text":"一点里有两点，一个事物包含有两个不同的侧面。","index":83,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"643e778227","type":"paragraph","text":"王蒙很有希望，新生力量，有文才的人难得。","index":121,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"64fcdbe09d","type":"paragraph","text":"现在的危险是以为天下太平了，因此看见王蒙的批评就不高兴。只是打，是锻炼不出文","index":72,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"668da09077","type":"paragraph","text":"胡适说，我是他的学生。他当教授，我当小职员，工资不一样，但我不是他的学生。","index":49,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"675fcff9d9","type":"paragraph","text":"当政党同人民的关系，不应当是老爷同人民的关系，不应该骂。","index":46,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6c19cfb382","type":"paragraph","text":"王蒙的小说有小资产阶级思想，他的经验也还不够，但他是新生力量，要保护，批评他的文章没有保护之意。","index":16,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d28c339d4","type":"paragraph","text":"没有爱情，人类就绝种。","index":112,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6df6e4c0f6","type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人，一年有一百万人闹事是正常的，六百分之一。","index":64,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f49273338","type":"paragraph","text":"青年人反对官僚主义不那么怕，因为他们还（没）有当事，官僚主义还未轮到他们头上。〕","index":117,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"711064b139","type":"paragraph","text":"闹事的人根本不能说是反革命，可能其中有个别反革命。","index":65,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"71aded858a","type":"paragraph","text":"是不是允许香花，不允许毒草存在？〔百花齐放应允许毒草存在，允许风格不同。〕","index":74,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73173f1542","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的官僚主义就是没有整垮，应该批评。过去有一个片子（指《荣誉属于谁》）没有演，那不是因为批评了老干部，要保护老干部，而是因为在那个片子里，那官僚主义没有整垮。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"78e30fbe0a","type":"paragraph","text":"要争鸣就要有准备。通过鸣来教育改造，而不是自由主义。一切不要一脚踢开，对错误要批评，也要承认二重性。〕","index":88,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7da744142d","type":"paragraph","text":"〔干部中真正搞通统一战线思想的人不多——要帮助人家改造，达到真正的团结。怎样帮助改造人家思想，很不够。办法常是整一通。“整”，很容易，但不是好办法，应不用。“整”，不能团结。〕","index":22,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"823130dde7","type":"paragraph","text":"三千年前，人类还用石头，以后进化到用铜铁，一直到用机器。人类历史五十万年，章太炎在“书”就讲过。铜器时代否定了石器时代，人类在地球上就是挖地皮过日子。谁也没有选举人类当地球的主人，许多动物，野兽没有选，细菌也没有选。大概只有植物才不反对我们。我们死了，可以供给植物养料，我们排泄的东西也可以供它们补用。","index":103,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"83df6fd441","type":"paragraph","text":"〔我们应特别（注意）到，掌握政权之后，想用简单的办法把人打倒。百花齐放为什么（有人）怕放？怕饭票子过河。","index":116,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8578612512","type":"paragraph","text":"〔用教条主义不能批评人家，因无力量，请看一下列宁是如何写《经验批制论》的。斯大林后来就不同了，不是平等讨论问题了，不是搜集大量材料发表意见。有些东西写得好，有些东西只坐在山岗上，拣起石头打人，使人看了后不大舒服。〕","index":39,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8581601599","type":"paragraph","text":"李希凡说王蒙写的地方不对，不是典型环境，说北京在中央。难道不可能出现这样的问题，这是不能说服人的。","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"85ab353b0d","type":"paragraph","text":"因为有问题，还是闹一下好。","index":62,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"85feba8982","type":"paragraph","text":"《星星》（四川的诗刊）里面有几首诗还是好的，有几首是不好的，要酝酿一下，不要骂。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"887a26ed3b","type":"paragraph","text":"党的统一战线政策，实际赞成的人很少，真正懂得的人很少，“整”，不能服人。","index":21,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8b30f2c35e","type":"paragraph","text":"说共产党的缺点不能揭发，这种观点不对。","index":20,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ed209e64d","type":"paragraph","text":"这些矛盾是暂时性的矛盾，不是根本性的矛盾。","index":68,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f8446fc45","type":"paragraph","text":"《文汇报》上姚文元的文章好。〔《教条与原则》很有说服力。〕","index":85,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96a653c8e1","type":"paragraph","text":"不要怕歪风。风总有两种，一歪一正。","index":108,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c2fb21434","type":"paragraph","text":"当然，有些东西是不能推翻的，如同说地球旋转而太阳不旋转，是地球绕看太阳转。而","index":100,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9cef3608c7","type":"paragraph","text":"对起义将领傅作义，对荣毅仁，我们都是帮助、改造。这样做了，他们就同我们合作。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9fb95dd014","type":"paragraph","text":"教条主义的方法，就是形而上学的方法。","index":80,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a30e771887","type":"paragraph","text":"坏小说，无非里面资产阶级思想，唯心论，只要作者在政治上同我们合作，就和胡风有区别，不能一棍子打死。","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a7d4395f3d","type":"paragraph","text":"李希凡现在在高级机关，当了政协委员，吃光饭，听党的命令，当了婆婆，写的文章就不生动了，使人读不下去。文章的头半截，使人读不懂。","index":36,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a89a089e26","type":"paragraph","text":"说老子是“老革命”不能反对。国民党也是“老革命”，比我们更老。我们不能采取国民党对人民的态度。","index":70,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ac3781ef4e","type":"paragraph","text":"教条主义不是马克思主义。","index":47,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b2b0f20fa3","type":"paragraph","text":"过去批评胡适，取得很大的成功，开头我们说，不能全抹煞胡适，他对中国的启蒙运动起了作用。康有为、梁启超也不能抹煞。","index":48,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b4875143c9","type":"paragraph","text":"他们就是怕闹事。","index":57,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b8a3806bd5","type":"paragraph","text":"王蒙有两重性，一是好处，一是缺点。","index":82,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b8bdb6384b","type":"paragraph","text":"（××：王蒙要求谈。）","index":119,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b9e5189584","type":"paragraph","text":"是啊，我们反杜林反了许多年，还不知道杜林是怎样的，可不可以找到杜林的书？","index":127,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1021291e8","type":"paragraph","text":"〔大学生中地富和资产阶级子弟占 80%，都是非工人阶级，青年问题多，并不奇怪。其中要搞匈牙利事变的极少，多数是拥护共产主义的。〕","index":28,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c17a16bd4a","type":"paragraph","text":"如何建设这样一个大国家，是马克思主义者的一个新问题。如何少走弯路？我们这样一个大国，六亿人口，马克思没有想到，列宁也没有想到，他建设社会主义国家也没有几年。","index":105,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c770fac694","type":"paragraph","text":"............","index":25,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c98515696c","type":"paragraph","text":"是有官僚主义。我们党的威望大，靠党的威望，官僚主义就横行霸道，违法乱纪，是不是应该揭发？","index":17,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf833a4282","type":"paragraph","text":"商品有二重性，王蒙也有二重性。","index":84,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d032ebb068","type":"paragraph","text":"②这是中央宣传工作会议之前主席召开的一次座谈会，对文、哲、教育界谈文化思想问题，着重谈文学批评问题。","index":132,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d10ecf94c4","type":"paragraph","text":"〔过去因为是斗争，所以讲缺点，今天也不必平反。今天他是帝国主义走狗。到二十一世纪，历史上还是要讲清楚的。〕","index":51,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d1f8b5368b","type":"paragraph","text":"〔王蒙的《组织部新来的年轻人》正在讨论，问题在于批评态度。小说揭发官僚主义，很好，揭发得不深刻，但很好。刘宾雁的小说并没有批评整个的官僚主义。王蒙的小说有片面性，正面的积极力量写得不够，要批评。应该有批评，也应该有保护。正面人物林震写得无力，而反面人物很生动。〕","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d4a4c7d7de","type":"paragraph","text":"现在王明还是有选票，他不还是中华人民共和国的公民，而不是一脚把他踢倒。","index":23,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d7f6470c16","type":"paragraph","text":"粮食地里有许多野草，庄稼是同野草作斗争才发展起来的。苏联建设了几十年社会主义，地里一样有野草。有野草不要紧，一翻过来，就是肥料。","index":76,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d957e11718","type":"paragraph","text":"对闹事的人不应当通通叫他们写悔过书，也不要写检讨。","index":61,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d9ad35bce7","type":"paragraph","text":"王蒙的小说有片面性，又有反官僚主义的一面，我看他的文章写得相当好，不是很好。","index":33,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d9ed977783","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的同志有教条主义，用片面性反对片面性，用形而上学反形而上学。","index":32,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da0d881d22","type":"paragraph","text":"不能说一切问题都解决了，还有很多问题要发现，要解决。","index":107,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"db086e33fa","type":"paragraph","text":"教条主义的文章干巴巴，简单化，不能说服人。","index":41,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc0fffaec2","type":"paragraph","text":"我们现在是以少数教育多数。","index":91,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dd9875e21d","type":"paragraph","text":"不能说以前都是教条主义。国民党曾经一家独鸣，所以打倒他们后，共产党也有一阵一家独鸣，这个一家独鸣是必需的，现在就不同了。","index":86,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e17a81d9f6","type":"paragraph","text":"陈其通、马寒冰等四人联名写的文章，后讲清楚原因，没有办法。陈沂，你写了几篇文章？有没有教条主义？出一个选集吧！全面检查一下。","index":40,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e2624055f7","type":"paragraph","text":"对那些写了坏作品的作者要帮助，要调查。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e34938c3b3","type":"paragraph","text":"当然，我也不登广告，提倡全国罢工。","index":67,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e349d22bd0","type":"paragraph","text":"是毒草，可以说明，有的人主张写：“此是毒草，不许尝试”。苏联的办法是只要香花，不要毒草。其实许多毒草是借香花之名以生。我们的主张是：毒草与香花齐放，落霞与孤鹜齐飞。","index":77,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e4269aa8b5","type":"paragraph","text":"〔李希凡的文章不能说服人，认为中央所在地的区委不会有官僚主义，是不对的。中央都出过高、饶，区委（有官僚主义）更不希奇了，“难免论”吗。（对林震也有些“难免论”。）","index":13,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e4eebbee50","type":"paragraph","text":"现在是大变的时期，有的人不满。农业合作化，富裕中农就不满。","index":27,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e521c0ea53","type":"paragraph","text":"将来没有阶级斗争，但有新的斗争。那时社会科学领域内总会有新的学说出来。","index":99,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7be908413","type":"paragraph","text":"教条主义滋长，是因为当了政。","index":42,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eba1db8cb2","type":"paragraph","text":"〔东欧出乱子，就是这原因。现在情况变了，必须百家争鸣。","index":87,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebf4840fa3","type":"paragraph","text":"对如何处理人民内部的错误的方针，很多同志实际没懂。对这个方针，十个部长大概有九个反对。","index":14,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ec35aa85b9","type":"title","text":"在颐年堂的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ede2c4ffc0","type":"paragraph","text":"现在就是碰不得官僚主义，好像骂官僚主义就是骂自己，好，你自己既然承认官僚主义，就得骂。","index":122,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eeed0b3104","type":"paragraph","text":"我们六亿人口，将来有一天上街，在大街上走都得排队。将来在街上会挤杀人，怎样分配报纸，怎样看电影，怎样逛公园，都会成问题。","index":106,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0344c4558","type":"paragraph","text":"马寒冰、李希凡的文章也有两重性，是教条主义，但可以促起注意。他们实际不赞成百花齐放、百家争鸣的方针。","index":94,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f118a5c4d2","type":"paragraph","text":"①（翻印说明：这一材料是根据三份传达记录稿整理而成，以一份记录稿为主，〔 〕内是根据另两份记录稿插入的。）","index":131,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f65022264c","type":"paragraph","text":"〔陈其通等四人的文章，立场很好，人民日报也可以发表，但是说服不了人，似乎百花齐放以后都错了，这是教条主义，朵朵香花是不可能的。教条主义是没有力量的，它所以滋长，原因之一是共产党当了政。马克思、恩格斯批评杜林，列宁批评卢那卡尔斯基，所以要下功夫，驳倒了他们。斯大林不同，（他当了政），所以他们批评不平等，很容易，像老子骂儿子。“一朝权在手，便把令来行”。批评不要利用当政的权力，需要真理，用马克思主义，下功夫，是能战胜的。〕","index":38,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6a37da0b4","type":"paragraph","text":"出了事情，要看两面。（闹事的人也有两面性，警惕我们。有脓疮，出脓就好了。）","index":69,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6b70c13bc","type":"paragraph","text":"人类也会被否定。有一天这样的人类不适合了，就一切毁灭，但这样对宇宙进化有好处。","index":102,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fbc8552856","type":"paragraph","text":"可以对大家讲清楚，不要仓促应战，不要仓促写文章。打仗，不是说不打无准备的仗，不打没有把握的仗吗？没有把握的也就是无准备的。现在打的仗也就是无准备的。","index":89,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"feaf0a61d1","type":"paragraph","text":"............","index":55,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ffc090cadf","type":"paragraph","text":"马寒冰是什么人？也是一个什么官长，总是一个什么军长级的干部吧，他在《文汇报》的文章就写得不好，教条主义。","index":37,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a5c3c09eaa","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":275,"end":266}}}},"__N_SSG":true}